Package net.sf.tweety.agents.sim

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AgentGenerator<T extends Agent,S extends MultiAgentSystem<T>>
    This interface defines an agent template that is used to generate agents following some common characteristics.
    GameProtocol
    Classes implementing this interface represent protocols for games in the game theoretic meaning.
    MultiAgentSystemGenerator<T extends Agent,S extends MultiAgentSystem<T>>  
    ProtocolGenerator<T extends Protocol,S extends Agent,R extends MultiAgentSystem<S>>
    Generates protocols for simulation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameSimulator<S extends AbstractProtocol & GameProtocol,T extends Agent,R extends MultiAgentSystem<T>>
    This class implements a game simulator.
    SimulationParameters
    Objects of this class store additional simulation parameters that should be shared among the generating components of a simulation.
    SimulationResult<S extends AbstractProtocol & GameProtocol,T extends Agent,R extends MultiAgentSystem<T>>
    Instances of this class summarize information on a performed simulation.
